 and continue to shape these environments. With photographs by Jacqueline Schlossman.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 15. Sep 2020) 0aNational parks and reservesxPolitical aspectszUnited States. 4aBig Bend. 4aBoquillas. 4aDeath Valley. 4aTimbisha Shoshone Homeland Act. 4aWilderness Act. 4aaffect theory. 4aborder studies. 4aenvironmental justice. 4afuturity. 4aspectacle. 7aPHILOSOPHY / Movements / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUP Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015z978311070398640uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978080479342140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780804793421423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780804793421.jpg  a978-3-11-070398-6  SUP Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015c2014d2015  aGBV-deGruyter-alles